Malaysia-Iran collaboration in these industries through their
joint exploration in third countries, Mustapha said.
</P>
<P>
He added that Iran also planned to make Malaysia a regional
distribution center for its oil.
</P>
<P>
The national oil companies of both countries have also agreed
to exchange information on the petroleum industry, he said.
</P>
<P>
Gholamreza is on a three-day visit to Malaysia.  
