the development of the Angolan peace process, because the Middle
East peace process is meeting with similar difficulties and is in
subtle situation.
</P>
<P>
He said that Israel wants to know how the Angolan government
will overcome these difficulties and bring final peace to their
country.
</P>
<P>
Referring to the Middle East peace process, he said his
country and Palestine are making positive efforts to find a way
of reopening negotiations between the two sides.
</P>
<P>
The Israeli vice-speaker arrived here on Tuesday to start his
three-day visit for enhance bilateral cooperation relations.
