China and the US should increase exchanges in various fields in
a bid to promote bilateral economic and trade cooperation, he
said. "A healthy and stable development of Sino-US ties not only
conforms to the fundamental interests of the two peoples, but is
also conducive to world peace and stability."
</P>
<P>
Wang appreciated the delegation's efforts at boosting economic
and trade cooperation between the State of Illinois and the
relevant Chinese provinces.
</P>
<P>
Maitland said that Illinois is ready to further increase its
cooperation with China in economic relations and trade, and hopes
that its economic exchanges and cooperation with relevant Chinese
provinces will continue to grow.
</P>
<P>
The US visitors have come to visit China as guests of the
Chinese People's Association for Friendship with Foreign
Countries.  
