durable solution is in the interest of its people, the region and
the world, " he said.
</P>
<P>
Asked about Islamabad' proposal for an intra-Afghan dialogue
and a UN-sponsored conference of regional countries on the Afghan
issue, Broujerdi said all matters relating to Afghanistan would
come up for discussion during his meetings with Pakistani
officials.
</P>
<P>
His visit to Pakistan was part of efforts of Islamabad and
Tehran to coordinate their work on the Afghan question, he said.
</P>
<P>
The Iranian minister said bilateral issues would also be
discussed at his talks with Pakistani officials.
</P>
<P>
Pakistan and Iran have agreed to hold regular consultations on
the Afghan issue.  
</P>
</TEXT>
